items.name: Distinguishing-Random-and-Ideal-Lattices-using-PCA-and-k-Means-Clustering
items.description: We use simple data science tools to distinguish weak lattice instances in post-quantum cryptography. Using features from 160 benchmark lattices, PCA and k-means clustering clearly separate random and ideal lattices. A lightweight script flags weak keys to improve cryptographic security.
